text: Wasim Zazai (born 3 March 1999) is an Afghan cricketer. He made his List A debut for Kabul Province in the 2019 Afghanistan Provincial Challenge Cup tournament on 31 July 2019. He made his Twenty20 debut on 8 September 2020, for Kabul Eagles in the 2020 Shpageeza Cricket League. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Afghan cricketers Category:Kabul Eagles cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
